org.mini2Dx.tiled.tileset

Class TsxTilesetSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.tiled.tileset.TilesetSource
      • org.mini2Dx.tiled.tileset.TsxTilesetSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Disposable

    public class TsxTilesetSource
extends TilesetSource
    A TilesetSource loaded from a TSX file. Allows for sharing data across multiple TiledMap instances.
